{"tid":582851,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【你今日留咗未？】九巴工潮：炒人後即出漫畫　指「停低休息吓啦」","createTime":"2018-03-06T13:37:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-06T14:10:21.000Z","uid":166571,"like":2,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"69164cdf1eb44003cbb7f53534bfa97df9bbc93c","tid":582851,"uid":166571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T13:37:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/06/213514_0ab996c3f24f841d4c64b85aca1d46d9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F06%2F213514_0ab996c3f24f841d4c64b85aca1d46d9.jpg&h=aa342c82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/06/213531_74d8cd04c96f0bb0e611e0792bbd1e69.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F06%2F213531_74d8cd04c96f0bb0e611e0792bbd1e69.JPG&h=e9e57477&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n又一公關災難？早前發起罷駛的九巴車長葉蔚琳遭解僱後，九巴Facebook專頁火速發貼，並附上一幅三格漫畫，當中出現「近排辛苦喇，停低休息吓啦！」的對白，遭網民瘋狂洗版留言，不少人揚言要罷搭九巴，亦有人反諷謂：「葉車長都要休息下喇」。<br />\n<br />\n漫畫以「九巴仔的日常- 城市要Go On」為題，講述有候車乘客主動關心滿頭大汗的助站務理「九巴仔」，說道︰<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>「近排辛苦喇，停低休息吓啦！」</strong></span>，惟「九巴仔」邊擦汗邊說︰「咁多人要返工返學，個城市唔停得架（㗎）！」<br />\n<br />\n不少網民將箇中對白，跟炒人一事扯上關係，旋即在該貼派嬲及留言。有網民<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>怒轟九巴「講一套，做一套」、「秋後算帳」</strong></span>；有人認為漫畫中的「停低休息」意思即是「炒人」，諷刺道：「真不愧貴公司可以攞到商界展關懷」，又質問：「炒咗仲點再花時間（跟車長）溝通？」貼文發出未夠一小時已獲過千個「嬲嬲」。<br />\n<br />\n早前為爭取車長權益而發起罷駛的「月薪車長大聯盟」召集人葉蔚琳，今天（6日）跟丈夫劉卓恆以及2名車長接獲解僱信。<br />\n---------------<br />\n《港呢啲》：大事小事騎呢事，東網嚴謹選題，輕鬆製作！<br />\n<br />\n畀埋link大家留言︰<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/kmbhongkong/photos/a.443884625669646.99026.439397589451683/1689354491122647/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fkmbhongkong%2Fphotos%2Fa.443884625669646.99026.439397589451683%2F1689354491122647%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=FkRYAJ%2BVlyd61e66YX%2B9U%2F7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=34041218\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/kmbhongkong/photos/a.443884625669646.99026.439397589451683/1689354491122647/?type=3&amp;theater</a>"},{"pid":"c5d73a50fbfbe9397a052fe75ca45fd3a9be54e1","tid":582851,"uid":15745,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T13:38:31.000Z","msg":"假仁假義"},{"pid":"5b8b3417f5c88389f44ec285f68af66174606cd4","tid":582851,"uid":3976,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T13:39:21.000Z","msg":"九巴死喇 叫習大大休息"},{"pid":"d87d64101d0c4c4865d861986ccd1821ee2c35f5","tid":582851,"uid":166571,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5b8b3417f5c88389f44ec285f68af66174606cd4","tid":582851,"uid":3976,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T13:39:21.000Z","msg":"九巴死喇 叫習大大休息"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T13:42:49.000Z","msg":"万刀甲ching你入去留咗言未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3326b36af9a2b22c9aee1a55ace9cd6ef85fef8d","tid":582851,"uid":166571,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"69164cdf1eb44003cbb7f53534bfa97df9bbc93c","tid":582851,"uid":166571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T13:37:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/06/213514_0ab996c3f24f841d4c64b85aca1d46d9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F06%2F213514_0ab996c3f24f841d4c64b85aca1d46d9.jpg&h=aa342c82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/06/213531_74d8cd04c96f0bb0e611e0792bbd1e69.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F06%2F213531_74d8cd04c96f0bb0e611e0792bbd1e69.JPG&h=e9e57477&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n又一公關災難？早前發起罷駛的九巴車長葉蔚琳遭解僱後，九巴Facebook專頁火速發貼，並附上一幅三格漫畫，當中出現「近排辛苦喇，停低休息吓啦！」的對白，遭網民瘋狂洗版留言，不少人揚言要罷搭九巴，亦有人反諷謂：「葉車長都要休息下喇」。<br />\n<br />\n漫畫以「九巴仔的日常- 城市要Go On」為題，講述有候車乘客主動關